fect for activities like running, cycling, working out, or binge-watching, they seamlessly combine safety, comfort, and performance.<\/p><p><span class=\"highlight\">Key Features<\/span><\/p><ul><li><strong>Open-Ear Design:<\/strong> Stay connected to your environment while enjoying superior sound quality.<\/li><li><strong>Ultra-Lightweight:<\/strong> Weighing just 24 grams, they offer unmatched comfort for long hours of use.<\/li><li><strong>Dual Pairing:<\/strong> Effortlessly multitask with seamless device switching.<\/li><li><strong>Extended Battery Life:<\/strong> Enjoy 12+ hours of use with quick charging capability.<\/li><li><strong>IPX5 Waterproof and Sweatproof:<\/strong> Built to withstand workouts and any weather conditions.<\/li><li><strong>No Sound Leakage:<\/strong> Keep your music private, even in public spaces.<\/li><\/ul><p><span class=\"highlight\">Health-Conscious Design<\/span><br>Certified by ENT specialists, these headphones reduce the risk of infections and ear canal damage, making them an excellent choice for extended use. Whether you need sports open-ear headphones, ambient sound headphones, or lightweight headphones with a mic, NG EarSafe Lite is the best choice for workouts and beyond.<\/p><p><span class=\"highlight\">Peace of Mind<\/span><\/p><ul><li><strong>Free Shipping<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>7-Day Return Policy<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>1-Year Replacement Warranty<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p><span><strong>Order Now<\/strong><\/span><br>Choose the smarter way to listen. Buy NG EarSafe Lite Open Ear Wireless Headphones today and experience unparalleled comfort and safety!<\/p><\/div><\/div><style>.accordion{width:450px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:15px}.accordion input{display:none}.accordion-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:5px 20px;color:#252525;cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;transition:background-color .3s ease}.accordion-label::after{c