outdoor adventures. These sporty open-ear headphones are built to withstand intense activities effortlessly.<\/p>"}},"template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-2":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Is NG EarSafe Lite compatible with Android as well as iOS?","content":"<p>Yes, these open-ear Bluetooth headphones work perfectly with all Bluetooth enabled devices, including Android & iOS smartphones, providing hassle-free connectivity for everyday use.<\/p>"}},"template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-3":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can anyone hear our conversations?","content":"<p>No, these open-ear wireless headphones are equipped with the latest anti-leakage technology that truly reduces sound leakage, ensuring your conversations stay private, even in calm or quiet surroundings.<\/p>"}},"8d42d8d4-8b59-4339-af47-78c859fa3f99":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Does it come with C-type charging?","content":"<p>Yes, NG EarSafe Lite comes with a C-type charging cable, providing fast and convenient charging. This feature ensures that your open ear earbuds are always ready for extended use.<\/p>"}},"a7ca32a8-e1ac-4b07-8789-786cf58f7140":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"It works on which open ear technology?","content":"<p>NG EarSafe Lite operates on air conduction technology, transmitting sound through tiny speakers positioned outside the ear. This lightweight open ear headphone design ensures ambient sound awareness while delivering clear audio.<\/p>"}},"f5707af2-5e96-4991-bbf6-cd7df09ebaec":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Can NG EarSafe Lite be connected with 2 devices at the same time?","content":"<p>Yes, these open wireless earbuds come with dual pairing support, letting you effortlessly switch between 2 devices. This feature is perfect for multitasking people, whether you are working out or cycling.<\/p>"}},"3d75943e-9fb9-483d-a299-2db3629ede4f":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"It looks like it sits on the ears. Does it go inside the ears?","content":"<p>No, NG EarSafe Lite rests gently on your ears and uses its open-ear design to provide clear Dolby sound. This keeps your ears open and safe, avoiding the ear canal discomfort commonly caused by earphones with rubber tips.<\/p>"}},"997edcc4-6546-4b4b-9f3f-2a58893a6493":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Is there a return and replacement policy?","content":"<p>We offer a 7-day no-questions-asked return policy and a 1-year doorstep replacement warranty for these comfortable headphones, ensuring long-term satisfaction for your open ear audio needs.<\/p>"}},"0fc5345d-97f9-47b2-8e24-8ec050136d74":{"type":"accor_item","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Is there any offer available?","content":"<p>Yes. Get a flat ₹200 instant discount on these highly-rated open ear wireless headphones for workouts when you pay through any prepaid method.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-1","template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-2","template--20627092865303__83a135b9-30ff-430d-a7ed-dd7da7224ef0-accor_item-3","8d42d8d4-8b59-4339-af47-78c859fa3f99","a7ca32a8-e1ac-4b07-8789-786cf58f7140","f5707af2-5e96-4991-bbf6-cd7df09ebaec","3d75943e-9fb9-483d-a299-2db3629ede4f","997edcc4-6546-4b4b-9f3f-2a58893a6493","0fc5345d-97f9-47b2-8e24-8ec050136d74"],"settings":{"design_heading":"1","heading_align":"t4s-text-center","top_heading":"Frequently Asked Question","icon_heading":"las la-gem","top_subheading":"","tophead_mb":30,"accor_des":"1","title_cl":"#222222","bg_title_cl":"#f6f6f8","title_active_cl":"#000000","bg_title_active_cl":"#f6f6f8","content_cl":"#878787","bg_content_cl":"#ffffff","content_align":"t4s-text-start","auto_active":true,"layout":"t4s-container-wrap","custom_width":1000,"cl_bg":